OL,3,CRecruitment under way to find next
OL,4,CNorthern Ireland victims' commissioner
OL,6,FA recruitment competition has been
OL,7,Flaunched to find Northern Ireland's
OL,8,Fnext commissioner for victims and
OL,9,Fsurvivors.
OL,11,FFormer commissioner Ian Jeffers
OL,12,Fstepped down at the start of January
OL,13,Fafter almost two years in the role.
OL,15,FHis successor could not be appointed
OL,16,Fin the then-absence of a functioning
OL,17,FStormont Executive, which returned in
OL,18,FFebruary.
