OL,3,CRecruitment under way to find next
OL,4,CNorthern Ireland victims' commissioner
OL,6,FThe commission has been run by its
OL,7,Fchief executive in the absence of a
OL,8,Fcommissioner.
OL,10,FThe office includes ensuring that
OL,11,Fservices for victims of Northern
OL,12,FIreland's troubled past are fit for
OL,13,Fpurpose.
OL,15,FOn Monday, First Minister Michelle
OL,16,FO'Neill and deputy First Minister Emma
OL,17,FLittle-Pengelly announced the opening
OL,18,Fof a recruitment competition for the
OL,19,Frole.
