OL,3,CRecruitment under way to find next
OL,4,CNorthern Ireland victims' commissioner
OL,6,FMs O'Neill said ensuring that victims
OL,7,Fand survivors have a strong
OL,8,Findependent voice is a "key priority"
OL,9,Ffor the Executive.
OL,11,F"The role of Commissioner is essential
OL,12,Fin supporting this and promoting the
OL,13,Finterests of victims and survivors,"
OL,14,Fshe said.
OL,16,F"We encourage anyone who feels that
OL,17,Fthey could fulfil the role to apply."
