OL,3,CRecruitment under way to find next
OL,4,CNorthern Ireland victims' commissioner
OL,6,FMs Little-Pengelly added: "The
OL,7,Fappointment of the new commissioner
OL,8,Ffor victims and survivors is essential
OL,9,Fto inform the development of policies
OL,10,Fand help ensure that the longer-term
OL,11,Fneeds of victims and survivors are
OL,12,Faddressed.
OL,14,F"We look forward to the new
OL,15,FCommissioner being in post to support
OL,16,Fthis important work."
OL,18,FThe closing date for applications is
OL,19,Fnoon on November 29.
